---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About WestGroup Financial Management - Fee-Only Financial Advisor Vancouver BC | Fiduciary Financial Planner BC"
  description="Learn about WestGroup Financial Management's experienced team of fee-only financial advisor Vancouver BC professionals. Fiduciary financial planner BC serving over 3000+ clients with comprehensive wealth management Vancouver and tax-efficient strategies."
  keywords="about WestGroup Financial, fee-only financial advisor Vancouver BC, fiduciary financial planner BC, licensed financial advisors Vancouver, wealth management Vancouver experience, financial planning credentials Vancouver, investment advisor Vancouver BC, retirement advisor Vancouver BC"
  canonical="https://westgroupfinancial.com/about"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-32 md:pt-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500/10 to-accent-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500/10 to-primary-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-custom mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="observe-scroll">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          <span class="text-white">About</span><br>
          <span class="gradient-text">WestGroup Financial</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Your trusted fee-only financial advisor Vancouver BC team, dedicated to building generational wealth 
          through transparent, comprehensive financial planning for high-net-worth families. As fiduciary financial planner BC professionals, we serve Vancouver, Surrey, and all of British Columbia.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">Schedule Consultation</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">View Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-dark-900/50">
    <div class="container-custom mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="observe-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
            <span class="text-white">Our</span>
            <span class="gradient-text"> Story</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Founded with a simple yet powerful mission: to provide transparent, fee-only financial advisor Vancouver BC 
            services that always put our clients' interests first as your fiduciary financial planner BC.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            We recognized that too many financial advisors were conflicted by commission structures that 
            prioritized product sales over client outcomes. As fee-only financial advisor Vancouver BC professionals and fiduciary advisors, we legally bound 
            ourselves to act in your best interest, creating a foundation of trust that has helped over 3000+ 
            families achieve their wealth management Vancouver and financial planning goals.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500/10 to-accent-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">15+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Years of Experience</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500/10 to-primary-500/10 border border-accent-500/30 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">3000+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Satisfied Clients</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="observe-scroll">
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-8 glow-effect">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Values</h3>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-primary-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-800" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Fiduciary Standard</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    We are legally bound to act in your best interest, providing transparent advice without conflicts.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-600 to-accent-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Expertise First</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Specialized knowledge in tax-efficient strategies and sophisticated wealth management techniques.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Long-term Relationships</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Building generational wealth through enduring partnerships with families and businesses.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Leadership Team Section -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-custom mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 observe-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          <span class="text-white">Meet Our</span>
