          <p class="text-accent-400 font-medium mb-4">Senior Portfolio Manager</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            15+ years specializing in portfolio management and risk assessment with deep expertise in 
            alternative investments and tax-loss harvesting.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-accent-500/20 text-accent-400 text-xs rounded-full">CFA</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-400 text-xs rounded-full">FRM</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-accent-500/20 text-accent-400 text-xs rounded-full">CAIA</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 3 -->
        <div class="card observe-scroll group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:animate-pulse">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">David Rodriguez, J.D.</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-400 font-medium mb-4">Estate Planning Specialist</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            20+ years combining legal expertise with financial planning, specializing in complex estate 
            structures and business succession planning.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-primary-500/20 text-primary-400 text-xs rounded-full">J.D.</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-accent-500/20 text-accent-400 text-xs rounded-full">LL.M</span>
